<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men zhǔn bèi hǎo yíng jiē dà fù xìng, nǐ kàn chē lún gǔn gǔn léi shēng lóng lóng.
 wàn guó jìng bài, dǎ gǔ jī qìng yé hé huá zài quán de bèi zūn chóng.
 duō shǎo lí xiāng bèi jǐng xiōng jiě men, zài yì guó jiē dào xiāng féng,
 yī qǐ huái niàn zǒu guò de rì zi, shén jīn tiān zhōng yú zuò chéng.
 zài shén fán shì dōu néng, yuǎn chù jìn chù dōu shì zàn měi shēng;
 zài shén fán shì dōu néng, yī qiè dōu zuò chéng.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men zhǔn bèi hǎo 迦南550</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>550</hymn_number>
</song>